readme:
# flutter package

A package for Atom that enables basic support for Flutter development.

The package itself is very much in development, and non-functional as of now.
Please excuse this as I work on it.

If you have an idea feel free to suggest it in the bug section.
>I am not taking pull requests just yet because of how early this is in development. Thank you for understanding.
